Notes: Array of 0-5 other damage/vehicle photos - Complex mapping based on slot position
First image (slot 0) - Maps to file_url_other_vehicle in incident_reports. Field name mismatch.
Second image (slot 1) - Maps to file_url_other_vehicle_1 in incident_reports. Field name mismatch.
Third image (slot 2) - Stored in user_documents table only. No incident_reports mapping.
Fourth image (slot 3) - Stored in user_documents table only. No incident_reports mapping.
Fifth image (slot 4) - Stored in user_documents table only. No incident_reports mapping.
Session ID for temp photo finalization - From sessionStorage, shared across all photo pages (4a, 6, 8)
Temp storage path from /api/images/temp-upload - Format: temp/{session}/{filename}
Original filename from File object - Stored for display and reference
Formatted file size (e.g., '1.2 MB') - For display only, not stored in DB. Raw size in bytes available in user_documents.file_size
Blob URL for preview (URL.createObjectURL) - Client-side only, not persisted. Memory cleanup on removal.
Field name for each image (slot-based) - Stored as document_type in user_documents
